reviewText: The course is really amazing. I could learn a lot, i suffered becuse it was challenging. I recommend it, definetely!
F​antastic course, I learned a lot. Many thanks to the instructors and the support team!

T​hank you Professors. This is a great course to gain hands-on knowledge of equity derivatives pricing (including some Exotics), credit derivative pricing (including some Exotics). There are also real options. It can be very frustrating to try to get the assignments correct. But when it happens, it is a big relieve and we have achieved to the next level. Appreciate all the efforts from Professors and teaching staffs!
